{"tid":1436623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2014年泛民維穩大台霸道實錄！","createTime":"2019-08-09T10:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:15:18.000Z","uid":241151,"like":15,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ab9cd4b99c0b19f49fba8c3e7f4c7dce3f994d","tid":1436623,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=q0YU9yuE1Ks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3Dq0YU9yuE1Ks&d=mdS8n1K3gC4RK9SJ0KjOqxV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=700490ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=q0YU9yuE1Ks</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2014年，何秀蘭議員助理陳小萍於金鐘佔領區發言：「大台已經成立，點解你地仲要挑戰佢？」引起在場人士嘩然，質問個大台係幾時成立。販民技倆就係要死攬住你，話你地都係大台一份子，如果你攻擊大台你就係鬼。<br />\n<br />\n雨傘革命中不少抗爭者都經歷過2014 販民點樣出賣民眾，所以點解一路以嚟要咁強調同泛民主派從來唔係同路人，叫佢地企開啲，因為佢地嘅本質就係出賣前線！"},{"pid":"18d9a6fdcc790c1b193993780679ca3c9df5770f","tid":1436623,"uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:25:25.000Z","msg":"根本現在有人想做大台亦無人理，但一天幾十個post講大台，目的好明啦！<br />\n<br />\n大家要合作，就算出到火，和理非不認同也沒有割，大家要合作，對準777打啦！"},{"pid":"609359d92f5bddafb7b92b9e3d86270e472db1fa","tid":1436623,"uid":263161,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:26:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea975feb4e9fd20e70999d6c1fb68b6278d498b3","tid":1436623,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"未睇片 留名加推一推先"},{"pid":"bd728b841721c637579b5aefea6d7c25285df3a7","tid":1436623,"uid":143718,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"樓主分化撚<br />\n建議block"},{"pid":"55e648cb4be82ef796173517996b74e8607c197e","tid":1436623,"uid":271199,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"大台只有一個，政府警狗，邊個話有大台就直接同佢講 我大台就係敵人<br />\n唔洗再討論大台post，唔洗再開大台post，全部大台post立即要完，集中討論正經post。"},{"pid":"ef1d489